{"tid":2478514,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港島2警涉派對房間犯聚被捕 「搞手」聲稱招待舊同學消遣","createTime":"2021-04-07T06:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T06:29:20.000Z","uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"129f5625d8dfd784e312753454f5c7a268b16396","tid":2478514,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始早前表示，由於酒吧、派對房間（party room）等屬防疫風險較高處所，現時仍須關閉，惟仍有人鋌而走險舉辦活動。消息指，兩名警員日前因在派對房間參與多人聚會，涉違反防疫規例被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當中一人為港島區機動部隊警員，為該中學同學聚會的「搞手」；另一人則為中區警區巡邏小隊成員。2人連同其他參加者於周一（5日）深夜遭東九龍總區重案組拘捕，並以涉違反限聚令票控。<br />\n消息指，涉事派對房間的持牌人為該「搞手」的家人，警方正調查該名警員是否有份經營該場地。據了解，他曾聲稱當時派對房間並非正在營業，只是以私人地方招待一班同學消遣，認為自己並無違例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/UHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FUHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=33042e9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FUHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA%2F&h=4d5b51ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/UHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA/</a>"},{"pid":"10b6058220ee22feb4333f3b94558cde89d96b87","tid":2478514,"uid":160592,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"就係會員 撚狗俠 同  Watchmen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8de100055710e5906039760c6907bef29aab99d","tid":2478514,"uid":34409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"129f5625d8dfd784e312753454f5c7a268b16396","tid":2478514,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始早前表示，由於酒吧、派對房間（party room）等屬防疫風險較高處所，現時仍須關閉，惟仍有人鋌而走險舉辦活動。消息指，兩名警員日前因在派對房間參與多人聚會，涉違反防疫規例被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當中一人為港島區機動部隊警員，為該中學同學聚會的「搞手」；另一人則為中區警區巡邏小隊成員。2人連同其他參加者於周一（5日）深夜遭東九龍總區重案組拘捕，並以涉違反限聚令票控。<br />\n消息指，涉事派對房間的持牌人為該「搞手」的家人，警方正調查該名警員是否有份經營該場地。據了解，他曾聲稱當時派對房間並非正在營業，只是以私人地方招待一班同學消遣，認為自己並無違例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/UHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FUHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=33042e9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FUHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA%2F&h=4d5b51ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/UHL35NIUXZBH5C2ELJSCECPORA/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"據了解，他曾聲稱當時派對房間並非正在營業，只是以私人地方招待一班同學消遣，認為自己並無違例。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁之前你班狗又拉陳淑莊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a661f22268341e37dbddf71e9de86cb652bd5e6","tid":2478514,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3037007b36047310b58e65cd0504286516ae455a","tid":2478514,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b6058220ee22feb4333f3b94558cde89d96b87","tid":2478514,"uid":160592,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"就係會員 撚狗俠 同  Watchmen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:24:25.000Z","msg":"死黑警"},{"pid":"804874153b18855cc699e9b0fc859be266994762","tid":2478514,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"兩隻黑警嗰啲藍屍朋友群埋啲狗度玩<br />\n真係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ha